node.text:
Rise, Tarnished.

#ELDENRING comes to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC Digital January 21, 2022.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 10, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
In the wake of the Shattering, a blight claimed the mind of many a creature and man. Beware their chaotic frenzy.

#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ELDEN RING'.

node.text:
Traveling to the dark corners of the Lands Between is often necessary and not always voluntary. 

#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ELDEN RING'.
Photo by ELDEN RING on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text.
Photo by ELDEN RING on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
Faith, knowledge – there are many forces that shape the world. Choose your masters with care.

#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text.
Photo by ELDEN RING on September 07, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'ELDEN RING'.
Photo by ELDEN RING on August 28, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
Tarnished who accept Melina's accord find fellowship here.
 
#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on August 27, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text.

node.text:
Dangers await those who trek for the ramparts of Stormveil.

#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on June 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'ELDEN RING'.

node.text:
A lord clings to his ruined Legacy; the ruler of a husk wrung dry by war.

#ELDENRING

node.text:
Foul deeds brought the Shattering to these lands. Fouler deeds yet may still be afoot. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.text:
The Lands Between are vast, but a Tarnished need not walk their path alone. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.text:
Like the Erdtree itself, a Tarnished's path reaches up to the branches of the heavens and twists down into the roots of the earth. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on June 14, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'ELDENR E DEN RING'.
Photo by ELDEN RING on June 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ELDENR RING'.

node.text:
The Lands Between basked in the pure light of the Greater Will before the Shattering. 

Slivers of its blessing yet remain in hidden pockets where lost graces wait to be found. #ELDENRING

node.text: “The importance we place on the joy the player experiences through overcoming challenges will be the same as it is in our other titles. I believe it will prove to be a very satisfying experience.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki #ELDENRING
